      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. It has been meticulously cared for, with a flawless exterior and an interior that is truly spotless. If you're looking for the highest quality possible, this is the one for you!",
