    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The exterior has multiple large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust spots on the wheel arches, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some missing trim pieces. It currently runs roughly and will likely need major engine or transmission repairs to be reliable for daily use; it is recommended for someone looking for a major project or a parts car.",
